Sets a random hostname from a wordfile at every shutdown
Created for and tested on Debian Sid
Written by auraltension 

INSTALLATION:
$ sudo cp hostnamerand.sh /etc/init.d/'
$ sudo chmod +x /etc/init.d/hostnamerand.sh'
$ sudo update-rc.d hostnamerand.sh stop 01 0 6'
Copy a wordlist to /usr/share/dict/hostnames
